  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575960/extras/589151ed80163650ae38b7fe0510d8af.avif?t=1745450093\" width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Aria was a cherished companion and lover.She died suddenly during an adventure.To atone for not being able to protect her, the protagonist wants to fulfill her wish: collect hatsukka flowers to express his gratitude!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575960/extras/4589166eec42b05d3e249271cd0eb58b.avif?t=1745450093\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575960/extras_big/4589166eec42b05d3e249271cd0eb58b.avif?t=1745450093 width=800 height=612 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Make her dreams come true</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel around town, looking for people who need help.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They need help fighting monsters, finding things, solving problems, and more.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help them and collect Hatsuka flowers!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575960/extras/25004c02d87b28d7ed1057e9d4d010a6.avif?t=1745450093\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575960/extras_big/25004c02d87b28d7ed1057e9d4d010a6.avif?t=1745450093 width=800 height=612 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Use different combinations to defeat enemies</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Party members come in a variety of classes, including warriors, rogues, mages, and more.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recruit party members from all over town and build your favorite combinations to take down your enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are a variety of attributes, such as fire, electricity, and darkness, that you can use to give you an advantage in battle.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575960/extras/38a61607821647af5bd8a990027ca5cc.poster.avif?t=1745450093\" width=800 height=610 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575960/extras/38a61607821647af5bd8a990027ca5cc.webm?t=1745450093\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575960/extras/38a61607821647af5bd8a990027ca5cc.mp4?t=1745450093\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A big world to explore</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ice caves, slime forests, ruins, underground caverns, and more.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare for adventure, explore, and immerse yourself in Hatsuka's world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575960/extras/bc13bed1896eaaa724c740975e852f40.poster.avif?t=1745450093\" width=800 height=610 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575960/extras/bc13bed1896eaaa724c740975e852f40.webm?t=1745450093\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575960/extras/bc13bed1896eaaa724c740975e852f40.mp4?t=1745450093\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575960/extras/589151ed80163650ae38b7fe0510d8af.avif?t=1745450093\" width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Aria was a cherished companion and lover.She died suddenly during an adventure.To atone for not being able to protect her, the protagonist wants to fulfill her wish: collect hatsukka flowers to express his gratitude!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575960/extras/4589166eec42b05d3e249271cd0eb58b.avif?t=1745450093\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575960/extras_big/4589166eec42b05d3e249271cd0eb58b.avif?t=1745450093 width=800 height=612 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Make her dreams come true</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel around town, looking for people who need help.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They need help fighting monsters, finding things, solving problems, and more.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help them and collect Hatsuka flowers!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575960/extras/25004c02d87b28d7ed1057e9d4d010a6.avif?t=1745450093\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575960/extras_big/25004c02d87b28d7ed1057e9d4d010a6.avif?t=1745450093 width=800 height=612 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Use different combinations to defeat enemies</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Party members come in a variety of classes, including warriors, rogues, mages, and more.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recruit party members from all over town and build your favorite combinations to take down your enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are a variety of attributes, such as fire, electricity, and darkness, that you can use to give you an advantage in battle.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575960/extras/38a61607821647af5bd8a990027ca5cc.poster.avif?t=1745450093\" width=800 height=610 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575960/extras/38a61607821647af5bd8a990027ca5cc.webm?t=1745450093\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575960/extras/38a61607821647af5bd8a990027ca5cc.mp4?t=1745450093\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A big world to explore</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ice caves, slime forests, ruins, underground caverns, and more.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare for adventure, explore, and immerse yourself in Hatsuka's world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575960/extras/bc13bed1896eaaa724c740975e852f40.poster.avif?t=1745450093\" width=800 height=610 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575960/extras/bc13bed1896eaaa724c740975e852f40.webm?t=1745450093\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575960/extras/bc13bed1896eaaa724c740975e852f40.mp4?t=1745450093\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>